1. Purpose of this file
Defines, in code:
Lunar phases as psychological tempo
Cognitive and emotional phenomenology per phase
Allowed and forbidden language per phase
Editorial usage guidance (what to do / not do)
Anti-prediction enforcement at the time layer
Used by:
Interpreter (Layer 2)
Editorial planner (Layer 3)
QA enforcement
Arc logic
No lunar language is allowed unless it conforms to this file.

